{"article_id":"u1sTo0M7xXslbdzx","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Key witnesses have renewed their definitive statements","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"that they did not see any of the sexual misconduct","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"that a few women have said","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"they suffered at the hands of Supreme Court nominee Judge Brett M. Kavanaugh ,","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"bolstering his case","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"as the FBI gets into the heart of its investigation .","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"President Trump made clear over the weekend","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"that he remains firmly behind Judge Kavanaugh","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"and urged voters to cast Republican ballots in key Senate races this year","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"to protest the \" angry and mean and nasty and untruthful \" approach","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"Democrats have taken toward the nomination .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Republicans on Sunday said","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"absent any major new revelations ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"senators on the fence are likely to vote to confirm Judge Kavanaugh .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"\" If there ' s some shocking new bit of , not accusation , but evidence and proof ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"then of course I ' m open to evaluating that evidence , \"","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"Sen. Tom Cotton , Arkansas Republican , said on CBS ' s \" Face the Nation. \"","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"\" But I strongly suspect","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"that every statement","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"that was made to the Judiciary Committee under penalty of perjury","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"is the exact same statement","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"that ' s going to be made to the FBI . \"","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"The FBI has until Friday to investigate claims by Christine Blasey Ford and other women","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"who have come forward","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"to claim","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"they were victims of sexual misconduct","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"that Judge Kavanaugh was involved in during his high school and college years .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"With those allegations swirling ,","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"Sen. Jeff Flake of Arizona forced fellow Republicans to delay voting on the judge ' s confirmation","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"in order to give the FBI time","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"to reopen the background investigation into Judge Kavanaugh .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"SEE ALSO :","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"House may have to investigate Kavanaugh","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"even if confirmed ,","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"top Judiciary Committee Democrat says","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"Democrats praised Mr. Flake","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"and excoriated Judge Kavanaugh ,","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"his indignant denials of allegations","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"-","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"which remain uncorroborated","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"more than two weeks after they began to surface -","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"rang hollow .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"Sen. Mazie K. Hirono , Hawaii Democrat , said","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"Judge Kavanaugh could have cleared up matters","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"if he had demanded","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"that the FBI reinvestigate himself .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"\" He could have helped us get over this whole issue of an FBI investigation , \"","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Ms. Hirono said on ABC ' s \" This Week.","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"\" \" He wouldn ' t go there .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"But finally , finally we ' re going to get one ,","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"and the question [ is ] are we going to get the kind of investigation","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"that is thorough and fair ? \"","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"Despite the allegations ,","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"Judge Kavanaugh has cleared his first hurdle .","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"The Senate Judiciary Committee voted 11-10 along party lines Friday","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"to advance the nomination to the full Senate floor .","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"But rather than a speedy vote there ,","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"action is stalled","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"while the FBI conducts its investigation of Ms. Blasey Ford ' s accusation","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"that Judge Kavanaugh pinned her down","depth":14},{"id":61,"text":"and tried to force himself on her at a party more than 35 years ago","depth":15},{"id":62,"text":"when they were both in high school ;","depth":15},{"id":63,"text":"Deborah Ramirez ' s claim","depth":14},{"id":64,"text":"that he exposed himself to her during an alcohol-fueled party at Yale University ;","depth":14},{"id":65,"text":"and Julie Swetnick ' s less-developed claim","depth":14},{"id":66,"text":"that Judge Kavanaugh was complicit in gang rapes of girls in high school .","depth":14},{"id":67,"text":"Judge Kavanaugh has strenuously and forcefully denied all the accusations","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"and has said","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"Ms. Swetnick ' s allegation is beyond the pale .","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"An attorney for Ms. Ramirez confirmed","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"she has been contacted by the FBI ,","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"but it ' s unclear whether Ms. Swetnick herself will be questioned as part of the inquiry .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"\" How do you conduct a legitimate , fair & thorough investigation into allegations","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"unless you interview the person","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"actually making the allegations about her experiences , what she witnessed , and what facts and other witnesses","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"she is aware of ?","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"Answer -","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"YOU CAN ' T .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"And that ' s by design , \"","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"Michael Avenatti , an attorney for Ms. Swetnick and frequent thorn in the side of Mr. Trump , tweeted Sunday .","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"Ms. Blasey Ford has identified three people","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"she says","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"were at the party","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"where she was assaulted ,","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"in addition to Judge Kavanaugh .","depth":5},{"id":86,"text":"None of those three has backed up her story .","depth":5},{"id":87,"text":"Indeed , Leland Keyser , a longtime friend of Ms. Blasey Ford , told the Judiciary Committee over the weekend","depth":6},{"id":88,"text":"that she stands by her statement","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"that she doesn ' t remember any such party","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"and doesn ' t recall even having met Judge Kavanaugh .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"Mark Judge , the man","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"Ms.","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"Blasey Ford says","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"was in the room","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"when she was assaulted","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"and who","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"Ms. Swetnick says","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"was part of the gang rapes ,","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"also said","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"he will cooperate with the FBI .","depth":6},{"id":101,"text":"He repeated his denial of any knowledge of those crimes .","depth":5},{"id":102,"text":"The New York Times reported","depth":5},{"id":103,"text":"that in addition to Ms. Ramirez and Ms. Keyser , the FBI will also likely question P.J . Smyth , another guest","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"Ms.","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"Blasey Ford says","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"was at the 1982 party .","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"Mr. Trump over the weekend stood by his nominee ,","depth":5},{"id":108,"text":"calling Democrats ' treatment of Judge Kavanaugh \" angry and mean and nasty and untruthful . \"","depth":5},{"id":109,"text":"The president was stumping for Patrick Morrisey , West Virginia ' s Republican attorney general ,","depth":6},{"id":110,"text":"who is seeking to unseat Sen. Joe Manchin III , a Democrat .","depth":6},{"id":111,"text":"Mr. Manchin is one of only two Democrats","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"who have not yet signaled plans","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"to vote against Judge Kavanaugh ' s confirmation -","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"but Mr. Trump said","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"Mr. Manchin is enabling the other Democrats ' attacks on the nominee .","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"\" I just hope","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"you don ' t sit home","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"because bad things will happen","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"if you sit home , \"","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"the president told a rabidly enthusiastic crowd .","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"Democrats on Sunday said","depth":7},{"id":122,"text":"Judge Kavanaugh should recuse himself from legal matters","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"involving congressional Democrats","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"if he is confirmed ,","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"citing his \" partisan \" performance during last week ' s hearing .","depth":7},{"id":126,"text":"\" His animus toward the entire Democratic Party , toward people","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"associated with it like the Clintons , should be disqualifying , \"","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"said Rep. Jerold Nadler , New York Democrat .","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"\" He showed no judicial temperament . \"","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"Mr. Nadler ,","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"who is in line","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"to become chairman of the Judiciary Committee","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"if Democrats take control of the House ,","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"said","depth":7},{"id":135,"text":"the House would continue to investigate a Supreme Court Justice Kavanaugh","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"if the Senate doesn ' t do a thorough job .","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"\" We would have to investigate any credible allegation , certainly of perjury and other things","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"that haven ' t been properly looked into before , \"","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"he said on \" This Week . \"","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"Republicans have said","depth":6},{"id":141,"text":"the performance from Judge Kavanaugh ,","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"who forcefully denied accusations of sexual assault and misconduct in high school and college ,","depth":8},{"id":143,"text":"rang true from someone","depth":8},{"id":144,"text":"who believes","depth":9},{"id":145,"text":"he has been wrongly accused .","depth":9},{"id":146,"text":"The judge said in his testimony last week","depth":7},{"id":147,"text":"that his opponents have engaged in a \" calculated and orchestrated political hit ,","depth":8},{"id":148,"text":"fueled with apparent pent-up anger about President Trump and the 2016 election . \"","depth":8},{"id":149,"text":"\" Fear","depth":9},{"id":150,"text":"that has been unfairly stoked about my judicial record .","depth":9},{"id":151,"text":"Revenge on behalf of the Clintons .","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"And millions of dollars in money from outside left-wing opposition groups , \"","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"he said .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":307,"left":234,"right":306,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":234,"left":159,"right":233,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":159,"left":157,"right":158,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":0,"right":156,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":1,"right":155,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":155,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":158,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":233,"left":183,"right":232,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":183,"left":163,"right":182,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"pare